KELLER WILLIAMS REALTY OF SOUTHEAST TEXAS-0600697

data.description: INSTANT EQUITY! Updated flooring. Never flooded per seller. This affordable home is located in the Bridge City School District. The 3-bedroom, 1 bathroom home had the roof replaced (2021).  There is a large Kitchen with custom cabinets, & dining area with wood burning fireplace. The semi open concept boasts a large living room/den combinations with big windows to illuminate the area on those sunny days. The sunroom provides extra space with potential galore. The garage features an area for the laundry, full bath with shower/tub, commode, sink and a window unit, great work bench. Backyard has plenty of room to roam. Two storage buildings on skids. With a fair offer, seller is willing to leave the refrigerator (relatively new) and the washer and dryer.  Make your appointment today.
